# PC/Mobile 분리
	## PC 

		### html4.01

			- html4.01 Transitional
				<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.01 Transitional//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/html4/loose.dtd">
				
				<meta http-equiv="content-type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" />
			
			- 지원 브라우저 : ie8, chrome, safari



			#### mark up common rule
				- closed empty elements
					HTML5 dose not require empty elements to be closed. But I want stricter validation, and need to make my document readable by XML parser, so I close all HTML elements properly.
					
				- lowercase tag 

	
				



